  "detail": {
    "tagExpireTime": "1765767979972",
    "endLabelIds": "",
    "endLabelNames": "",
    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台店铺经营主体变更规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1302542657244119040",
    "content": "<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 20.15pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">您好，为适应业务发展和满足商家主体变更需求，对</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=910870419488247808\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">《京东开放平台店铺经营主体变更规则》</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">进行调整。现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年12月8日- 2025年12月14日，规则预计于2025年12月15日生效，公示期满后平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 20.15pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心调整点：1、新增可变更主体场景-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">同法人或法人之间为亲属关系（夫妻、父母子女及亲兄弟姐妹关系）</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">；2、需具备一般纳税人资格经营类目范围调整；3、取消确认函与承诺函资质，改为线上签署；4、取消变更次数限制；5、新增<span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">完成主体变更，需缴纳技术服务费200元条款。</span> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">具体调整内容如下：</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; background: white; border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 19.85pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">调整点</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"35%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 19.85pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第三条</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"35%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">新增（五）转让方与受让方为同法人或法人之间为亲属关系（夫妻、父母子女及亲兄弟姐妹关系）。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第三节 第十三条</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"35%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">类目要求。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">删除。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十四条</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"35%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">经营以下类目受让方主体需具备一般纳税人资格，具体如下表。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\">经营电脑软件类目，</span></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">受让方主体需具备一般纳税人资格要求</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">。</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第三章</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"35%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">主体变更操作流程。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">删除。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十六条</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"35%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（三）主体变更确认函（加盖转让方及受让方公司红章），模板见京麦后台-店铺-主体变更；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（四）主体变更承诺函（加盖转让方及受让方公司红章），模板见京麦后台-店铺-主体变更。</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">删除。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十九条</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"35%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家若变更主体，需要提前7天面向消费者说明变更事宜。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" width=\"40%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">删除。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二十条 </span> </span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">一个自然年度同一店铺仅允许申请一次店铺主体变更。 </span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">删除。</span> </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 23.86%; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">相关说明 </span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 35.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40.42%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">新增：若商家完成主体变更，需缴纳技术服务费200元。 </span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">修订后规则全文如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东开放平台店铺经营主体变更规则</span></strong></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 17pt 0cm 16.5pt; text-align: center; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 24pt; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第一章&nbsp;适用范围及定义</span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第一条&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本规则适用于入驻京东开放平台JD.COM的企业店铺。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二条</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">主体变更相关定义</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（一） 店铺主体变更：</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">指京东开放平台店铺在平台经营过程中，符合一定条件变更其店铺经营主体的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（二） 转让方和受让方：</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">转让方是指目前正在经营中的京东开放平台店铺公示的企业；受让方是指店铺变更主体完成后店铺所公示的企业。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（三） 控股人：</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">指持有公司超过50%股权或股份的主体。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（四） 实际控制人：</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">指通过投资关系、协议或者其他安排，能够实际支配公司行为的主体。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（五） 品牌商体系内公司：</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">指商标权利人以及与商标权利人存在控股或实际控制关系的公司。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（六） 品牌代理商：</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">指取得商标权利人授权开设店铺开展经营的主体。</span></span></p>\n<h1 id=\"heading-1\" style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 24pt; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二章&nbsp;主体变更相关要求</span></spa