yle=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（四） 受让方为京麦服务市场运营服务商，具体以</span></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\"><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://pro.jd.com/mall/active/BS2GQd3ofj9AGHHSJaqzpxmkKfX/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">JDM服务市场</a></span></u></span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">公示的名单为准。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（五） 转让方与受让方为同法人或法人之间为亲属关系（夫妻、父母子女及亲兄弟姐妹关系）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第四条&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">转让方及受让方均无正在被有权机关调查/诉讼或仲裁/品牌方投诉的情形。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第五条&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">转让方不存在拖欠京东费用的情况，包括但不限于京东开放平台保证金、服务费等。如转让方已开通京小贷服务，则还需结清对应店铺的京小贷欠款（包括但不限于信用贷、提前收款、极速收等服务）。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第六条&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">受让方须在京东开放平台开设并成功启用企业店铺且无&ldquo;非诚信经营&rdquo;记录。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第七条&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">受让方公司主体需要是正常经营存续状态。</span></span></p>\n<h2 id=\"heading-3\" style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 18pt; font-family: 宋体; font-weight: bold;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二节 店铺要求</span><